description:
In this karaoke video, I'm singing the song "Lead Me To Calvary"  This song is a classic and a favorite of mine, so I wanted to make a video of me performing it!

If you're looking for a karaoke video that will bring tears to your eyes, then look no further! This song is perfect for a tear-jerking night in with friends. 

Title: Lead Me to Calvary
Author: Jennie Evelyn Hussey (1921)
Music performed  by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters youtube channel
